detaileddescription.para: Initialize the BGAPI classes for btmesh stack.
This function is automatically called by code generated by the Universal Configurator if the feature is included in the project. The application is not expected to call this function directly.

parameterdescription.para: NULL-terminated array of pointers to class declarations. The array must remain valid until the next system reboot.

simplesect.para: SL_STATUS_OK if the initialization was successful; Other error code indicates a failure.
